content=["<dl>",
"<dt><a href='#Section0'>acromegaloidism or pseudo-acromegaly</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section0'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> Clinical features do not reliably differentiate the condition from acromegaly.",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> Insulin-like growth factor 1 normal.Random GH below 0.4 microgram/L (&lt;0.4 nanograms/mL).Oral glucose tolerance test (OGTT) nadir GH below 1 microgram/L (&lt;1 nanogram/mL).Fasting blood sugar and/ or OGTT glucose levels may be markedly elevated.</p>",
"</dd>",
"</dl>"].join("\n");